data.description: This charming and beautifully updated townhome offers a comfortable and stylish living space with 3 beds and 2 baths. The interior features new luxury vinyl flooring throughout, creating a modern and low-maintenance atmosphere. The kitchen boasts newer appliances and quartz countertops, adding a touch of elegance to the space. With tall ceilings and an open floorplan, the home feels spacious and inviting. The shiplap fireplace adds a cozy and trendy focal point to the living area, perfect for relaxing evenings. Additionally, the built-in office area provides a convenient workspace, combining functionality with the overall design. This townhome is a delightful blend of modern updates and classic charm, creating a welcoming environment for its residents. Won't last long! Located w/easy access to E470, Southlands Mall and DIA.
